testimony delivered by four men and two women 
the nearly twohour session covered atrocities and the 
destruction of kuwaits economy and infrastructure it was a 
prelude to thursdays meeting when the council is expected to 
authorize the use of military force to liberate kuwait if iraq does 
not withdraw by jan 15 
at tuesdays session the kuwaiti refugees including doctors a 
