an administrative law judge recommended 
rejection tuesday of the proposed 25 billion merger between san 
diego gas amp electric co and southern california edison saying the 
deal would create a monopoly 
officials of both companies immediately said they would 
challenge the recommendation by george p lewnes an administrative 
